---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations, useTranslatedPath } from '../i18n/utils';
import { Sparkles, BookOpen, Anchor, Map, Ship } from 'lucide-astro';

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
const translatePath = useTranslatedPath(lang);

const title = lang === 'zh' ? '岛屿故事 — 传承与陪伴' : 'Island Story — Heritage & Companionship';
const description = lang === 'zh'
  ? '探索 Captain Mora 与莫里的七年远航纪事。'
  : 'Explore the seven-year voyage of Captain Mora and Mori.';

const years = [
  {
    id: 'y1',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y1「启航」' : 'Y1 "The Voyage Begins"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '你不是一个人出发的' : 'You are not starting alone',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y1_prologue.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“光，是这样从一个人，传到另一个人的.”'
      : '"Light is passed on from one person to another."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '出发那天，莫拉船长走进了海里。这是他最后一次下水，也是莫里第一次出发。三十个故事，三十颗星纹，记忆从此苏醒。'
      : 'The day they set out, Captain Mora walked into the sea. It was his last time in the water, and Mori\'s first departure. Thirty stories, thirty stars, memories awakened.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y2',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y2「远潮」' : 'Y2 "Distant Tides"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '迷路是走进了没有名字的地方' : 'Getting lost is finding the unnamed',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y2_prologue.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“那边，你能走多远，就走多远.”'
      : '"Go as far as you can go over there."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '莫里在雾里看见年轻时的莫拉船长。他走进了一条没有名字的路。在那片没有被地图标注的水里，他看见了什么是真正的传承。'
      : 'Mori saw a young Captain Mora in the mist. He walked a road without a name. In those uncharted waters, he understood the true meaning of heritage.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y3',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y3「回响」' : 'Y3 "The Echo"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '你知道有人在，所以敢往前走' : 'You dare to move forward knowing they are there',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y3_prologue.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“今天自己出发. 你自己都知道.”'
      : '"Starting today on your own. You know it yourself."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '龟脊树长出了第一片叶子。莫里开始自己选择方向，因为他知道，无论走到哪里，岛都在那里，船长也都在身后。'
      : 'The Spineback Tree grew its first leaf. Mori began choosing his own paths, knowing the island and the Captain were always behind him.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y4',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y4「沉钟」' : 'Y4 "The Sunken Bell"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '越深的地方，越有光在等着' : 'The deeper you go, the more light waits',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y4_prologue.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“你去了比我更深的地方.”'
      : '"You have gone to a place deeper than I have."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '下潜，直到光芒消失。莫里下潜超过船长。在万年沉寂的深渊，他找到了那盏灯，并让沉寂已久的古钟再次震动整片海洋。'
      : 'Diving until the light vanished. Mori dove deeper than the Captain. In the eternal silence of the abyss, he found the lamp and made the ancient bell resonate through the ocean.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y5',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y5「古龟族」' : 'Y5 "The Ancient Kin"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '旧的东西，在新人手里才重' : 'Old things gain weight in new hands',
    image: '/v2/chapters/chapter_y5_prologue.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“你是一段很长的故事的一部分.”'
      : '"You are part of a very long story."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '七位先祖的影子显现，留下一张残缺的星图。一段被遗忘的历史在莫里手中重新连接，他不再只是他自己，他是历史的延续。'
      : 'Silhouettes of seven ancestors appeared, leaving a fragmented star map. A forgotten history reconnected in Mori\'s hands; he was no longer just himself.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y6',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y6「守岛」' : 'Y6 "Guardian"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '知道如何看着另一个人' : 'Knowing how to watch over another',
    image: '/v2/scenes/mori_at_island.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“他抓着一块漂木. 莫里认得. Y3 推回的那块.”'
      : '"He was holding a piece of driftwood. Mori recognized it. The one pushed back in Y3."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '辛塔漂流而至。莫里看着他，用了一个熟悉的眼神——那是莫拉船长当年看他的眼神。陪伴者，终成引路人。'
      : 'Cinta drifted ashore. Mori watched over him with a familiar gaze — the same one Captain Mora once gave him. The companion became the guide.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y7',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y7「黎明」' : 'Y7 "The Dawn"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '出门散个步，灯塔交给你了' : 'Going for a walk, the lighthouse is yours',
    image: '/v2/scenes/mori_lighthouse.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“灯塔交给你了.”'
      : '"The lighthouse is yours."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '时之雾彻底散去。莫拉船长留下一封信，莫里接过了守望者的责任。黎明已至，光将永远照亮这片海。'
      : 'The Time Mist cleared completely. Captain Mora left a letter, and Mori took over the responsibility of the watcher. Dawn has arrived, and light will forever illuminate the sea.'
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-24 space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 glass rounded-full text-xs font-black text-brand-blue uppercase tracking-widest animate-fade-in">
           <Sparkles size={14} /> <span>The Seven Years Epic</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black dark:text-slate-100 tracking-tight">
          {lang === 'zh' ? '七年，一光' : 'Seven Years, One'} <span class="text-gradient">{lang === 'zh' ? '传一光' : 'Light'}</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
          {lang === 'zh'
            ? '这是一个关于陪伴、成长与传承的故事。莫里在莫拉船长的指引下，从沙铃滩出发，穿过时之雾，直到点亮整片海洋。'
            : 'A story of companionship, growth, and heritage. Guided by Captain Mora, Mori sets off from Sandbell Shoal, through the Time Mist, until the entire ocean is lit.'}
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="relative space-y-32">
        <!-- Center Line (Desktop) -->
        <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-blue/20 via-brand-green/20 to-transparent -translate-x-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>

        {years.map((year, index) => (
          <div class={`relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 ${index % 2 === 1 ? 'md:flex-row-reverse' : ''}`}>
            <!-- Image Card -->
            <div class="flex-1 w-full group">
              <div class="glass-frame p-2 organic-radius overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.02] group-hover:-rotate-1">
                <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden organic-radius">
                  <img src={year.image} alt={year.title} class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110" />
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity flex flex-col justify-end p-8">
                     <p class="text-white font-bold italic text-lg leading-relaxed">{year.quote}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Indicator Dot -->
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-12 h-12 glass rounded-full hidden md:flex items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-xl border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-900">
               <div class={`w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-${year.color} animate-pulse`}></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Content Card -->
            <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-center md:text-left">
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <span class={`text-sm font-black text-${year.color} uppercase tracking-widest`}>{year.title}</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black dark:text-slate-100">{year.subtitle}</h2>
              </div>
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                {year.content}
              </p>

              <div class="pt-4 flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-4">
                <div class="px-4 py-2 glass rounded-xl flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                   {index === 0 ? <Anchor size={16} /> : index === 3 ? <Ship size={16} /> : <Map size={16} />}
                   <span>{index === 0 ? 'Departure' : index === 3 ? 'Deep Dive' : 'Exploration'}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Final CTA -->
      <div class="mt-48 text-center glass rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-24 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-green/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-1000"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 space-y-10">
           <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black dark:text-slate-100 leading-tight">
             {lang === 'zh' ? '点亮你的' : 'Light Up Your'} <br /><span class="text-gradient">{lang === 'zh' ? '星纹之路' : 'Starshell Path'}</span>
           </h2>
           <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-xl mx-auto font-medium">
             {lang === 'zh'
               ? '属于你的七年史诗才刚刚开始。莫里在等你，莫拉船长也在等。'
               : 'Your seven-year epic has only just begun. Mori is waiting, and so is Captain Mora.'}
           </p>
           <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6">
              <a href={translatePath('/') + '#download'} class="px-10 py-5 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-3xl font-black text-lg shadow-2xl shadow-brand-blue/20 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all">
                {lang === 'zh' ? '把小海龟带回家' : 'Bring Mori Home'}
              </a>
              <a href={translatePath('/gallery')} class="px-10 py-5 glass rounded-3xl font-black text-lg hover:bg-white/60 dark:hover:bg-gray-800/60 transition-all">
                {lang === 'zh' ? '查看视觉画廊' : 'View Gallery'}
              </a>
           </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative Background Image -->
        <img src="/v2/scenes/mori_lighthouse.webp" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000 pointer-events-none" alt="" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
